MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

97-988. Cooper v. United Parcel Serv.

Franklin App. No. 96APD06-824. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Franklin County. Upon consideration of the application for dismissal by the Industrial Commission of Ohio,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the application for dismissal by the Industrial Commission of Ohio be, and hereby is, granted.

The appeal of United Parcel Service remains pending,
